Mittal Weighs Buying More QPR Shares From Ecclestone, FT Reports

-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 
2011-05-14T07:17:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-14/mittal-weighs-buying-more-qpr-shares-from-ecclestone-ft-reports.html
Lakshmi Mittal is “thinking about”
taking up the option to buy more shares in west London football
club Queens Park Rangers from Formula One’s  Bernie Ecclestone ,
the  Financial Times  reported, citing an interview with Mittal.  The chief executive officer of  ArcelorMittal (MT) , which owns a
33 percent stake in QPR, said he was yet to discuss the matter
with Ecclestone, the FT said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sarah Jones in London at 
 sjones35@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
 arummer@bloomberg.net  